[SN]TITLE[SN]
The rules of touch rugby

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Touch rugby is a really fun game and is great way to get involved in the sport of rugby.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Media playback is unsupported on your device
11 September 2015 Last updated at 08:20 BST
Find out how many players you need to form a team, the rules of possession of the ball and everything else you need to know.
Sammie Phillips, the head coach of Maidenhead RFC Mohawks, took time out of training the team to explain all the rules.
